\begin_layout Standard

\series bold
4
\series default
.
 
\emph on
Proposition
\emph default
.
 For 
\begin_inset Formula $a\in\mathbb{F}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $v\in V$
\end_inset

, if 
\begin_inset Formula $av=0$
\end_inset

, then 
\begin_inset Formula $a=0$
\end_inset

