\begin_layout Standard

\series bold
15
\series default
.
 
\emph on
Proposition
\emph default
.
 If 
\begin_inset Formula $U_{1}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $U_{2}$
\end_inset

, and 
\begin_inset Formula $W$
\end_inset

 are subspace of 
\begin_inset Formula $V$
\end_inset

 such that 
\begin_inset Formula $V=U_{1}\oplus W$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $V=U_{2}\oplus W$
